attributes.title: Don’t Download!!!
attributes.review: I downloaded this app because my grandma is a fan of Trump. After creating an account for her the app kept asking for my location and I said no. The app said if I don’t access my location they will take my grandma. I thought it was a joke so I said no. These strange people barged into my house moments later and took my grandma. All of them bent down with there butts facing me and farted very loudly. Green fart gas filled the air and I was chocking on it. One of the strange people took a large poop in my toilet and and my whole house smelt like diarrhea. They left poop stains all over the toilet. After that they told me that I should have accessed my location. They said they tracked me down and installed cameras in my house, and that the FBI is going to be watching me. They loaded my grandma into a car and drove off. I haven’t seen my grandma for a week and the poop stains and stench is still in my house.
